-- Petrochina to Advise Partners of China Ruling on Arrow Acquisition `Soon'
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-13T03:50:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/petrochina-to-advise-partners-of-china-ruling-on-arrow-acquisition-soon-.html

          
          
             PetroChina Co. will advise its
partners of the Chinese goverment’s decision on whether to
approve the takeover with Royal Dutch Shell Plc of Australia’s
Arrow Energy Ltd. “very soon.”  
 PetroChina spokesman Mao Zefeng made the comment by phone
from Hong Kong today.  
          
          


  


        